# Telegram Bot

## 建立一個bot

首先在Telegram尋找@BotFather後，輸入`/newbot`建立新的bot；@BotFather會依序詢問要建立的bot的name(名稱)，及username(ID)，完成後便會取得API token

也可以對@BotFather對話還進行bot的設定，如換頭像或是刪除bot

![Alternative Text][1742374977448]

接著就可以點擊訊息中的`t.me/newtelegrambot_2HsBBUx90d_bot`與剛建立好的機器人進行對話。

## 取得訊息傳送者的id

透過`https://api.telegram.org/bot{API token}/getUpdates`來取得對話紀錄，結構大致如下


這邊可以從`from`下`id`取得剛剛傳送訊息者的id

## 傳送訊息

透過`https://api.telegram.org/bot{API token}/sendMessage?chat_id={傳送對象的id}&text={訊息文字}`來傳送訊息給指定的人

## 範例程式碼

下面是簡單程式範例，取得對話紀錄並傳訊息給最後一個傳訊息來的人

```csharp
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Data;
using System.Linq;
using System.Net;
using System.Net.Http;
using System.Threading.Tasks;
using System.Web.Script.Serialization;
using static ConsoleApp1.Program.TelegramBot;

namespace ConsoleApp1
{
    class Program
    {
        static void Main(string[] args)
        {
            Task t = Task.Run( async () =>
            {
                TelegramBot tb = new TelegramBot("7628332927:AAFBwfmO4y2xINlJ3dVhN9Zcqjxs_xfAhRs");
                
                //取得對話紀錄
                List<TelegramMessage> mlist = await tb.GetMessages();
                foreach (TelegramMessage tm in mlist)
                {
                    Console.WriteLine("date:{0} from_id:{1} from_first_name:{2} text:{3}", tm.date.ToString(), tm.from_id, tm.from_first_name, tm.text);
                }

                //傳送訊息給最後一個對話的人
                if (mlist.Count > 0)
                {
                    await tb.SendMessage(mlist[0].from_id, "Hello, " + mlist[0].from_first_name);
                }
            });
            t.Wait();
        }


        public class TelegramBot
        {
            /// <summary>
            /// 訊息
            /// </summary>
            public class TelegramMessage
            {
                public Int32 date { get; set; }
                public string from_id { get; set; }
                public string from_first_name { get; set; }
                public string text { get; set; }
            }

            private HttpClient client = new HttpClient();
            private string API { get; set; }

            /// <summary>
            /// 建構
            /// </summary>
            /// <param name="api"></param>
            public TelegramBot(String api)
            {
                //設定SecurityProtocol，較低的版本可能會無法連線
                ServicePointManager.SecurityProtocol = SecurityProtocolType.Tls12;

                this.API = api;
            }

            /// <summary>
            /// 取得對話紀錄
            /// </summary>
            /// <returns></returns>
            public async Task<List<TelegramMessage>> GetMessages()
            {
                try
                {
                    //取得最新的訊息
                    string url = $"https://api.telegram.org/bot{this.API}/getUpdates";
                    HttpResponseMessage response = await client.GetAsync(url);
                    response.EnsureSuccessStatusCode();
                    string responseBody = await response.Content.ReadAsStringAsync();

                    //解析JSON
                    JavaScriptSerializer js = new JavaScriptSerializer();
                    var json = js.Deserialize<dynamic>(responseBody);

                    //建構訊息
                    List<TelegramMessage> MessageList = new List<TelegramMessage>();
                    foreach (var result in json["result"])
                    {
                        TelegramMessage m = new TelegramMessage
                        {
                            date = Convert.ToInt32(result["message"]["date"]),
                            from_id = Convert.ToString(result["message"]["from"]["id"]),
                            from_first_name = Convert.ToString(result["message"]["from"]["first_name"]),
                            text = Convert.ToString(result["message"]["text"])
                        };
                        MessageList.Add(m);
                    }
                    MessageList = MessageList.OrderByDescending(x => x.date).ToList();

                    //回傳
                    return MessageList;
                }
                catch (Exception ex)
                {
                    Console.WriteLine(ex.Message);
                    return null;
                }
            }

            /// <summary>
            /// 傳送訊息
            /// </summary>
            /// <param name="chat_id"></param>
            /// <param name="text"></param>
            /// <returns></returns>
            public async Task SendMessage(string chat_id, string text)
            {
                try
                {
                    //傳送訊息
                    string url = $"https://api.telegram.org/bot{this.API}/sendMessage?chat_id={chat_id}&text={text}";
                    HttpResponseMessage response = await client.GetAsync(url);
                    response.EnsureSuccessStatusCode();
                    string responseBody = await response.Content.ReadAsStringAsync();
                }
                catch (Exception ex)
                {
                    Console.WriteLine(ex.Message);
                }

            }
        }
    }
}
```
